title: Kamala Harris and Hillary Clinton Rally Women to Support Hochul
description: Representative Lee Zeldin and Republicans nationally want to “turn back the clock on women’s rights,” Mrs. Clinton said at the Manhattan rally.
dc:creator: Michael Gold

media:content.media:credit: Kenny Holston for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: In the late stages of the New York governor’s race, Gov. Kathy Hochul is re-emphasizing the historical nature of being the state’s first female governor.
